          "question": "<p><a name=\"461028\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>​​​A rectangle has a length \\( L \\) and a width \\( W, \\)&nbsp; where \\( \\mathrm{L}&gt;\\mathrm{W} \\). If the width, \\( W, \\) is increased by \\( 10 \\% \\), which one of the following statements is correct for all values of \\( L \\) and \\( W? \\)</p></div><br><br><b>GATE DA 2025 | GA Question: 5</b></p>",
